Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然有关贤者之石的书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在都找不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个教主拿着的又是颗假货
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样又没有线索了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先回一趟中央吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼金术入门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着吧 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可是说要送我礼物的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以现在正做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是我们最初的炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就须要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时 我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}妈妈……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉 是你不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们俩特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小爱德华和小阿尔方斯可是为了你才这么做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么学 大部分人都是半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那两个孩子已经是不错的炼金术师了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是那两个孩子 应该对炼金术一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然 是他们父亲的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们俩是什么时候找爸爸学的炼金术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他人又不在 怎么找他学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们看了他的书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么难的书你们能看懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们做错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 你们很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈要去向大家夸耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}书一定要放回原处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸回来后一定要谢谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 不许打开那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸没有告诉我们要去哪里就出门旅行去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈越来越频繁地眺望远方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 从我们开始学炼金术以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她就越来越多地露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈一直称赞我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的心完全融入了炼金术里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还只能做出这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们俩真厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是你们父亲的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸也会夸奖我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 回来的话一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去温莉那儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你讨厌爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与其说讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}实际上都记不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次提到他的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈她…表情就变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就是讨厌这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们去温莉那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸和妈妈都死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 你父亲他们不是医生么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 所以他们参加了伊修巴尔战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉 我们的爸爸也是一样不在的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不一样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死掉的人是不会再回来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会再也回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在书里读到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一种人造人Homunculus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(720,48)\fs35}原意为小矮人 也指人头脑内部的另一个"自己"  这里的意思是利用炼金术造出的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然好像只是没有心的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用炼金术的话 你父亲他们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 那是不允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼金术不是万能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才有我们机械铠技师存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臭老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉 好可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都是大孩子了 会被人笑话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回来晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的病已经不是一天两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经忍耐病痛好几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些是寄给那家伙的信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果给这里所有的寄信人写信的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有谁知道爸爸在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就叫他赶快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可没想让他回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸…留下来的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没有动过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就靠这笔钱 你们俩好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说什么啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼成点什么给我吧 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 就要些花束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你爸爸…总是…给我做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈看到炼金术就会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实是因为想起了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把妈妈…变回原样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看 那家伙的私人笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然还不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是写着跟人体炼成有关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能解读这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 上面写了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人体炼成是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能让死人复活的话谁都会高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是因为谁都没能成功而心有不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大人们才禁止这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我和阿尔能重新跟妈妈一起快乐地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈一定也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 还是先问问爸爸为好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈的死都是那家伙的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈一直都在等着那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他却连葬礼都没来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那家伙没做成的事 我要…我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们找到了一个师父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重新学习炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水35升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}碳20千克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氨水4升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石灰1.5千克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}磷800克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盐250克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}硝石100克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氟7.5克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铁5克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}硅3克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}构成一个成年人身体的元素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结构式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再加上灵魂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就应该可以唤回妈妈的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并能把它和肉体相结合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在了还说什么呀 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 炼金术不是等价交换么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽说集齐了肉体的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈的精神用什么来交换呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题的 伸出手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灵魂的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这下就齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始吧 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是利森普尔村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 不太对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔————!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最后看见的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是哥哥左腿分解逐渐消失的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我到底出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 你的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用这一条右臂 只能把你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}固定在这铠甲上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 妈妈也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不是…人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥的理论应该是完美的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理论是没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}错的是…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆 救救…救救哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是…阿尔么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们修炼回来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说你们想要造出妈妈来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此 是人体炼成的光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从没见过这么强烈的炼成反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}军人到这里有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如你所见 这两个孩子受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我收到了这么一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是哥哥给爸爸的朋友的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们的父亲 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也找了他很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也不知道他们父亲的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有病人 你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但若是有人进行了人体炼成却还能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我对此比找到他们的父亲还要感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能会成为一名不错的国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快回去 我们忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是国家炼金术师罗伊·穆斯唐中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们可以来中央找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…早上好 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆 家里有我攒下来的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傻瓜 那种小事别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用那笔钱 给我造一副机械义肢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去前两天见到的那个罗伊那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此我需要能自由活动的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你莫非都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从师父那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为国家炼金术师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以读到由国家管理的贵重文献
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还可以获得预算 自由地进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 那块怀表还可以让炼金术师的力量增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老师没有这么说么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果战争爆发的话就会被迫去参战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果有命令的话 本该为大众服务的炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就会夺取人们生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夺去我孩子们生命的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据说就有国家炼金术师参与
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做军队的走狗还是什么的我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有一定要做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德 你还…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我做的最好的零件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧的 别进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让人吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把神经一根一根连接起来的剧痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连成年人都会忍不住发出惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟他比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很久没打了 来练练吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了锻炼精神 要先锻炼肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师父是这么说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 阿尔 你那样的身体没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会输给机械铠的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你真的打算成为国家炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不清楚能不能当得成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先去找那个叫罗伊的人看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的话我去当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你还想炼成妈妈么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时你不是说了么 我们错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后找到让哥哥的手脚复原的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不用考虑那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我当时反对的话 你就不会失去左腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了固定我的灵魂 连手臂也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒是你 身体怎么能一直那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把你变回原样的方法 我要找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈呢…就算了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概 能和妈妈的灵魂等价交换的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这世界上是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且…我不想连你都失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的话我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我不跟去的话 哥哥马上就会偷懒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来是因为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再一次跟你分开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是为了恢复自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们追求禁忌的人体炼成的心还是没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失败的话 下次可能就会从这世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管还会得到如何比这更残酷的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都无法再回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 踏上旅途的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们把家烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱的炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人偶依附了生命时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类就会明白自己的愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此还是不停地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}期望爱也能够炼成…
